===Adjective===
{{en-adj|er}}

# {{lb|en|of a person}} [[regretful|Regretful]] for an action; [[grieved]] or [[sadden]]ed, especially by the loss of something or someone.
#: ''I am '''sorry''' I stepped on your toes. It was an accident.''
#: ''I am '''sorry''' to hear of your uncle's death.''
# Poor, [[pitiful]]ly [[sad]] or [[regrettable]].
#: ''The storm left his garden in a '''sorry''' state.''
# [[pathetic#Adjective|Pathetic]] and [[inferior]] to the point of causing others disgust.
#: ''Bob is a '''sorry''' excuse for a football player.''

